[normal]Written evidence submitted by Christine Lord (BTO0003)[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Has the threat of ongoing transmission of 
[normal]vCJD
[normal] through blood and blood product supply been adequately mitigated?
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Here is my reply and experience 
[normal]I
[normal] am also offering myself as witness to the inquiry committee. 
